method.name: emulation_isis_network_group_config
method.description: This procedure creates/modifies/deletes ISIS route(s) to a particular simulated ISIS router Ixia Interface. The user can configure the properties of the ISIS routes.

description.text: This option represents the handle the user *must* pass to the "emulation_isis_network_group_config" procedure. This option specifies on which ISIS router to configure the ISIS topology. The ISIS router handle(s) are returned by the procedure "emulation_isis_config" when configuring ISIS routers on the Ixia interface.
Mode of the procedure call. Valid choices are: create modify delete.
The type of topology route to create.
